{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015EjxwFN3UuTNmuZXPSuFmP","type":"tool_result","content":"{\"id\":\"cloche-2sg\",\"title\":\"Add post-run log archival with SQLite indexing\",\"description\":\"On run completion, extract all log files from container to .cloche/\\u003crun-id\\u003e/output/. Write index entries to SQLite (run ID, step name, log file path, size, timestamps). Dashboard and CLI query index and serve file contents on demand. Enhance cloche logs \\u003crun-id\\u003e --step \\u003cname\\u003e filtering. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §4.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Logs extracted and archived on completion. SQLite index populated. cloche logs --step filtering works.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:19.148963423-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.857300137-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.857300137-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-2sg\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-v5x\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.662096666-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-9ea\",\"title\":\"Project versioning: increment .cloche/version on evolution changes\",\"description\":\"After the evolution pipeline makes any change to workflow or prompt files, increment the integer in .cloche/version. File starts at 1 (created by cloche init). See docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-versioning-design.md.\",\"design\":\"docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-versioning-design.md\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- .cloche/version is created with content '1' by cloche init\\n- config.LoadVersion(projectDir) reads and returns the version\\n- evolution/orchestrator.go increments the version when len(result.Changes) \\u003e 0\\n- Version is exposed in /api/projects/{name}/info response\\n- .cloche/version is not gitignored\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:03.406211132-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.138606886-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.138606886-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-e97\",\"title\":\"Fix update-docs step failing with 'prompt too long'\",\"description\":\"The update-docs step fails because assemblePrompt() in internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go injects all .cloche/output/*.log files as 'Validation Output' via readFeedback(). By the time update-docs runs, implement.log (full Claude stream-json, 50KB+) is in the output dir, blowing past the context limit. The feedback injection is designed for the fix step but fires indiscriminately for all agent steps.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- update-docs step completes without 'prompt too long' error\\n- fix step still receives validation feedback\\n- Make feedback opt-in: add a step config key (e.g. include_feedback=true) to control whether readFeedback() output is injected into the prompt\\n- Only the fix step should set include_feedback=true in the default workflow template\\n- Default is no feedback injection when the key is absent\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T12:50:31.844072218-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.789030545-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.789030545-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-jj7\",\"title\":\"Chore: add host.cloche and scripts/ to cloche project\",\"description\":\"After cloche-dzz merges and is installed, create .cloche/host.cloche and .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh in the cloche project, matching the default templates from cloche init. Restart cloched so it picks up the new orchestration workflow. Verify that the next orchestration cycle uses the host workflow path.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- .cloche/host.cloche exists with the default orchestrate workflow\\n- .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh exists and is executable (0755)\\n- Both files are committed\\n- cloched restarted; next orchestration cycle logs show host workflow execution\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:26.803760641-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.433838658-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.433838658-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-jj7\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.174588443-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-m8u\",\"title\":\"Workflow view: clicking steps shows filename but doesn't load contents\",\"description\":\"In the project page workflow view, clicking on a step shows the filename of the prompt file or script file, but doesn't actually load and display the file contents.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T19:16:51.84063528-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T19:56:49.043686554-08:00\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-mjj\",\"title\":\"Prompts section expansion shows git commits instead of file contents\",\"description\":\"In the project info page, clicking the expansion arrows in the Prompts section shows a list of git commits instead of showing the actual file contents.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T19:16:53.291876084-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T19:56:49.086420332-08:00\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-mk9\",\"title\":\"Chore: rename .cloche/config to .cloche/config.toml in cloche project\",\"description\":\"After cloche-2cc merges and is installed, the daemon will look for .cloche/config.toml. Rename our own project's config file to match, verify the daemon reads it correctly, and commit the rename.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- .cloche/config.toml exists with the same contents as the old .cloche/config\\n- .cloche/config is deleted\\n- cloched reads orchestration settings correctly after restart\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:26.677558038-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.211015766-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.211015766-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-mk9\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2cc\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:47.855916156-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.7\",\"title\":\"Update cloche init for subdirectory layout\",\"description\":\"Rewrite cmdInit to scaffold into ./cloche/ directory. Create cloche/.cloche/prompts/ instead of prompts/. Write Dockerfile and workflow into cloche/. Update workflow template file() paths to .cloche/prompts/. Add addGitignoreEntries helper to append cloche/.cloche/*/ and .gitworktrees/ to host .gitignore.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:19.110834041-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.365771012-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.365776312-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.7\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:19.112178441-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.7\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.3\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:19.114094259-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-s1j\",\"title\":\"Add dedicated /projects/{name} page\",\"description\":\"Create a dedicated project detail page at /projects/{name} with three panels: orchestrator control, project info, and workflow view. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md for full design.\",\"design\":\"docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- /projects/{name} route exists and renders\\n- Project cards on landing page link to /projects/{name}\\n- Orchestrator panel shows enabled/disabled status, in-flight count, concurrency; toggle and override work\\n- Project info panel shows docker image, version, prompt file git history with diff on click\\n- Workflow view renders steps and wires as a DAG; clicking a step opens a drawer with prompt/script content\\n- New API endpoints: GET/POST /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator, GET /api/projects/{name}/info, GET /api/projects/{name}/workflows\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:03.347821436-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-s1j\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-8zs\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.130988517-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-mjj\",\"title\":\"Prompts section expansion shows git commits instead of file contents\",\"description\":\"In the project info page, clicking the expansion arrows in the Prompts section shows a list of git commits instead of showing the actual file contents.\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"labels\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T19:16:53.291876084-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T20:44:56.763682779-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01L8HuAFH84UiejecX1Ag1xY","session_id":"c346fded-e5bd-469d-af11-5003